content: I got the Paid version of this because I liked the Unpaid version quite well but just didn't want the watermark on my image. With the Paid version, there is no watermark! Yay! My only remaining criticisms of the Paid version is:  1. There needs to be a delay up to 10 seconds. Right now you get: 1 sec, 2 sec, or 0 sec delay. Better than nothing, but I wish there were further options. 2. Saving a GIF that was created from an outside source video takes quite a long time still.  Others have complained about the Square aspect ratio, but you can disable that once in Camera mode. You get 1:1 and 3:4 ratio. If you want to shoot a longer GIF set, that's done in the main Settings and I LOVE that feature. A max fame set of 202 results in quite a long GIF, nearly like a short video clip really.  The filters and the frames are nice. The stickers are dumb, but that's just personal preference. I don't personally have a use for the Text feature (text over the GIF) but I could see how others would like that.   I wish I could give like a 4.75 out of 5 stars because I'd like an  extended Timer feature. Other than that, this App is freaking great!
